{"word":"διεγγυάω","slug":"διεγγυάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διεγγυάω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/>of persons, in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to give bail for</i> another, and in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to take bail for</i> him, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be bailed</i> by any one, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}